## Description

OpenVoiceOS plugin for Microsoft Azure

## Install

```bash
pip install ovos-stt-plugin-azure
```

## Configuration

```json
  "stt": {
    "module": "ovos-stt-plugin-azure",
    "ovos-stt-plugin-azure": {"key": "xxx", "region": "westeurope"}
 }
```


